    <string name="invoice_advice_legal_help">Click on me…!</string>
    <string name="invoice_advice_legal_1">Welcome to 𝕘𝟠 aka The Gate!\n\n I\'m Little Horseshoe, your new amigo ♡ \n\n You can click on me whenever you see me, I give \n\n …</string>
    <string name="invoice_advice_legal_2">useful information. You are currently in the "Invoices" category.\n\n Before creating an invoice, I recommend you check the \n\n …</string>
    <string name="invoice_advice_legal_3">mandatory information for a compliant invoice. To make your life easier, I\'ve summarised everything here: \n</string>
    <string name="invoice_advice_legal_4">the-gate.fr \n</string>
    <string name="invoice_advice_legal_5">\n On another note…</string>
    <string name="invoice_advice_legal_6">the documents you create, as well as all your changes, are saved automatically in the background. \n\n 𝕓𝕖𝕔𝕒𝕦𝕤𝕖 𝕚𝕞 𝕒 𝕓𝕒𝕥 𝕓𝕠𝕤𝕤</string>
    <string name="invoice_advice_legal_url">https://www.the-gate.fr/factures-et-bons-de-livraison-mentions-obligatoires</string>
    <string name="invoice_advice_bottom_menu">Hey hey, your batmagotchi here. I absolutely need to show you a trick \n\n …</string>
    <string name="invoice_advice_bottom_menu1">To reveal very useful options, like deleting a document \n\n …</string>
    <string name="invoice_advice_bottom_menu2">click on the circle ○ next to the invoice number. You can even select multiple documents at once.\n\n 𝕨𝕚𝕝𝕕</string>
    <string name="delivery_note_advice_convert">I learned this move in hip-hop, super cool I know. I still need to practice, I\'m not super fast, I think my patagium slows down the wave. Anyway, I wanted to tell you \n\n …</string>
    <string name="delivery_note_advice_convert1">that if you want to convert one or more delivery notes into an invoice, you can select them from the list by long pressing (or by clicking on the ○) \n\n …</string>
    <string name="delivery_note_advice_convert2">and click on "Invoice". It will appear in the "Invoices" tab at the top of the list with the number incremented from the previous invoice. \n\n 𝕡𝕣𝕒𝕚𝕤𝕖 𝕞𝕖</string>
    <string name="alert_dialog_delete_invoice_1">Are you sure? \n\nIf you have already sent the invoice, it is not legal to delete it: \n• if it has not yet been paid, you must create a corrective invoice \n• if it has been paid, you must create a credit note &amp; a new invoice.</string>
    <string name="document_product_advice">To edit a product, click on the grey box…</string>
    <string name="document_product_advice_2">The change only applies to this document…</string>
    <string name="document_product_advice_3">It does not affect the product saved in the "Products" tab.</string>
    <string name="alert_dialog_delete_invoice_2">Learn more\n</string>
    <string name="alert_dialog_delete_invoice_3">\nIn any case, deletion is irreversible.</string>
    <string name="alert_dialog_delete_url">https://www.the-gate.fr/supprimer-ou-annuler-une-facture</string>
    <string name="alert_dialog_delete_general">Are you sure? This action is irreversible.</string>
